  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Liz Truss to become UK\u2019s next prime minister",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "ECONOMYNEXT \u2013 The UK\u2019s Foreign Secretary Liz Truss is set to become the country\u2019s next prime minister after she was named leader of the ruling Conservative Party, international media reported.",
        "Truss\u2019 appointment as Tory leader, announced Monday September 05 afternoon, comes at a time when the UK is facing a recession.",
        "After weeks of an often bad-tempered and divisive party leadership contest that pitted Truss against\u00a0Rishi Sunak, a former finance minister, Monday\u2019s announcement triggered the beginning of a handover from\u00a0Boris Johnson, Al Jazeera reported Monday afternoon. (Colombo/Sep05/2022)"
      ],
